{"id":103002,"date":"2024-03-25T19:54:59","date_gmt":"2024-03-25T19:54:59","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/tal.bh"},"modified":"2024-03-26T15:25:30","modified_gmt":"2024-03-26T15:25:30","password":"","slug":"cover-design-faq","status":"publish","type":"docs","link":"https:\/\/spines.com\/docs\/cover-design-faq\/","title":{"rendered":"FAQ"},"content":{"rendered":"<div\n\tclass=\"betterdocs-faq-wrapper layout-modern icon-after  betterdocs-shortcode\">\n\t<h2 class=\" betterdocs-faq-section-title\"><\/h2>\n\t<div class=\"betterdocs-faq-inner-wrapper\">\n\t\t<div class=\"betterdocs-faq-title\">\n\t<h3 class=\"betterdocs-faq-title-tag\">Cover design FAQ<\/h3><\/div>\n<ul class=\"betterdocs-faq-list\"><li><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-group\"><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-post\">\n\t\t<p class=\"betterdocs-faq-post-name\">\n\t\tHow do I start designing my book cover?\t<\/p>\n\t<svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconminus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"stroke-width=\"2\"><g fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconplus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><g stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\"><path d=\"M12 7v10M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><\/div>\n<div class=\"betterdocs-faq-main-content\" >\n\t<p>Begin by describing your book and selecting the target audience age group that best suits your book. Our AI will then generate a few cover options for you automatically.<\/p>\n<p><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/li><li><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-group\"><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-post\">\n\t\t<p class=\"betterdocs-faq-post-name\">\n\t\tCan I provide input about myself for the cover design?\t<\/p>\n\t<svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconminus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"stroke-width=\"2\"><g fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconplus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><g stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\"><path d=\"M12 7v10M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><\/div>\n<div class=\"betterdocs-faq-main-content\" >\n\t<p>Yes, in the &#8216;About the Author&#8217; section, you can share your interests, experiences, and what makes you unique. This information will be used to generate the biography of your book for the back cover.<\/p><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/li><li><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-group\"><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-post\">\n\t\t<p class=\"betterdocs-faq-post-name\">\n\t\tIs it possible to regenerate the author bio and back cover text?\t<\/p>\n\t<svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconminus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"stroke-width=\"2\"><g fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconplus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><g stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\"><path d=\"M12 7v10M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><\/div>\n<div class=\"betterdocs-faq-main-content\" >\n\t<p>Yes, you can click the &#8216;Regenerate&#8217; button to get different versions of your bio and back cover text, and further customize the text to your liking.<\/p><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/li><li><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-group\"><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-post\">\n\t\t<p class=\"betterdocs-faq-post-name\">\n\t\tWhat if I want to use my own design for the cover?\t<\/p>\n\t<svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconminus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"stroke-width=\"2\"><g fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconplus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><g stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\"><path d=\"M12 7v10M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><\/div>\n<div class=\"betterdocs-faq-main-content\" >\n\t<p>You can upload your own design by clicking on \u2018upload ready cover\u2019. Ensure your file is a single PDF that includes the back cover, spine, and front cover. The recommended file size is up to 40MB, with a maximum of 100MB.<\/p><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/li><li><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-group\"><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-post\">\n\t\t<p class=\"betterdocs-faq-post-name\">\n\t\tHow does the AI generate book cover designs?\t<\/p>\n\t<svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconminus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"stroke-width=\"2\"><g fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconplus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><g stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\"><path d=\"M12 7v10M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><\/div>\n<div class=\"betterdocs-faq-main-content\" >\n\t<p>The AI generates several options for your book cover based on your book title, description, author bio, and back cover text. You can choose the best fit and explore more options by clicking the &#8216;Regenerate&#8217; button.<\/p><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/li><li><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-group\"><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-post\">\n\t\t<p class=\"betterdocs-faq-post-name\">\n\t\tCan I manually edit the book cover?\t<\/p>\n\t<svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconminus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"stroke-width=\"2\"><g fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconplus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><g stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\"><path d=\"M12 7v10M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><\/div>\n<div class=\"betterdocs-faq-main-content\" >\n\t<p>Yes, you can make manual adjustments to the cover design, including changing the cover image, adjusting the design properties, and adding text or other elements like images, shapes, arrows, and lines.<\/p><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/li><li><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-group\"><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-post\">\n\t\t<p class=\"betterdocs-faq-post-name\">\n\t\tWhat are the customization options for text on the cover?\t<\/p>\n\t<svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconminus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"stroke-width=\"2\"><g fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconplus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><g stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\"><path d=\"M12 7v10M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><\/div>\n<div class=\"betterdocs-faq-main-content\" >\n\t<p>You can choose different fonts, sizes, and colors, and adjust properties such as opacity, background color, stroke, shadow, and blur. Text can be edited by double-clicking on it or selecting the pen icon.<\/p><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/li><li><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-group\"><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-post\">\n\t\t<p class=\"betterdocs-faq-post-name\">\n\t\tHow can I adjust the cover image?\t<\/p>\n\t<svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconminus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"stroke-width=\"2\"><g fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconplus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><g stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\"><path d=\"M12 7v10M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><\/div>\n<div class=\"betterdocs-faq-main-content\" >\n\t<p>You can adjust the brightness, contrast, hue, saturation, blur, and warmth of your cover. Additionally, filters can be added to your image to achieve the desired effect.<\/p><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/li><li><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-group\"><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-post\">\n\t\t<p class=\"betterdocs-faq-post-name\">\n\t\tWhat happens if I need to edit objects that are on top of each other?\t<\/p>\n\t<svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconminus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"stroke-width=\"2\"><g fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconplus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><g stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\"><path d=\"M12 7v10M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><\/div>\n<div class=\"betterdocs-faq-main-content\" >\n\t<p>If there are two objects on top of each other, you can select the desired item by clicking once on the side of the screen and then clicking on the item you want to modify.<\/p><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/li><li><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-group\"><div class=\"betterdocs-faq-post\">\n\t\t<p class=\"betterdocs-faq-post-name\">\n\t\tHow do I finalize my book cover design?\t<\/p>\n\t<svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconminus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"stroke-width=\"2\"><g fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><svg class=\"betterdocs-faq-iconplus\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><g stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#528ffe\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\"><path d=\"M12 7v10M17 12H7\"><\/path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><\/div>\n<div class=\"betterdocs-faq-main-content\" >\n\t<p>Once you&#8217;re satisfied with the design, click &#8216;Next&#8217;. Remember, you can always access the last image you selected by clicking on the &#8216;Previously chosen&#8217; button. Once you&#8217;re ready, your cover will be complete.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<\/p><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/li><\/ul>\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"doc_category":[197],"doc_tag":[],"class_list":["post-103002","docs","type-docs","status-publish","hentry","doc_category-cover-design"],"acf":[],"year_month":"2026-02","word_count":8,"total_views":"1308","reactions":{"happy":"5","normal":"0","sad":"10"},"author_info":{"name":"Spines","author_nicename":"spinesadmin","author_url":"https:\/\/spines.com\/author\/spinesadmin\/"},"doc_category_info":[{"term_name":"Cover Design","term_url":"https:\/\/spines.com\/docs-category\/cover-design\/"}],"doc_tag_info":[],"knowledge_base_info":[],"knowledge_base_slug":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/spines.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/docs\/103002","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/spines.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/docs"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/spines.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/docs"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/spines.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/spines.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=103002"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/spines.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/docs\/103002\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/spines.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=103002"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"doc_category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/spines.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/doc_category?post=103002"},{"taxonomy":"doc_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/spines.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/doc_tag?post=103002"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}